<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT14">
<l>nārā yaṇaṉeṉṉai yāḷi narakattuc</l>
<l>cērāmaṟ kākkun tirumāltaṉ pērāṉa</l>
<l>pēcap peṟāta piṇaccamayar pēcakkēṭ</l>
<l>ṭācaippaṭ ṭāḻvār palar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Listening to the words of the cadaver[-like] people [of other] religions,</l>
<l>—who did not get to utter the names of Tirumāl, [called] Nārāyaṇa,</l>
<l>He who rules me, He who protects [one] from reaching hell—</l>
<l>many [people] will sink, feeling the desire [to follow them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
